    "sections": {
        "description": "<p>This lightweight plugin makes Bible references on your website interactive, showing a preview when the visitor clicks or moves the mouse cursor over the references. Up to three verses are shown, followed by a &#8216;Read more&#8217; link.</p>\n<p>You can choose from 20+ languages and 50+ bible versions. Check the list of available languages/bibles <a href=\"https://bible-link.com/languages-and-translations/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">here</a>.</p>\n<p><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"750\" height=\"422\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/c-i_3ALvw-0?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://bible-link.com/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">bible-link.com</a></p>\n<h3>Contribute</h3>\n<p>Suggestions for improvements, additional functionality or more Bible translations are <a href=\"https://bible-link.com/contribute\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">welcome</a>.</p>\n<p>By installing this plugin you agree to <a href=\"https://bible-link.com/terms-of-use/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">these terms</a>.</p>\n",
        "installation": "<p>In WordPress:<br />\n1. Navigate in the wordpress admin to plugins-&gt;add new.<br />\n2. Search for &#8216;BibleLink Multilingual&#8217; by GlobalRize.<br />\n3. Install and activate the plugin.<br />\nNote: by installing the plugin you <a href=\"https://bible-link.com/terms-of-use/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">agree to the terms</a> for the use of the plugin.</p>\n",
        "changelog": "<h4>1.0.18</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Compatible with WordPress 6.6</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.17</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed incorrect fallback value</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.16</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Rolled back to 1.0.12, because of major bug</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.12</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Compatible with WordPress 6.1</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.11</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed compatability bug</li>\n<li>Plugin options won&#8217;t be deleted upon deactivation</li>\n<li>Compatible with WordPress 6.0</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.10</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed excluded class</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.9</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Compatible with WordPress 5.9</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.8</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Updated plugin page (wordpress.org)</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.7</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Added exclude class option</li>\n<li>Removed error notice in debugmode</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.6</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Changed the way additional languages options are stored.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.5</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Load plugin options external (languages, translations)</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.4</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Added Bible translation: ESV</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.3</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Added Bible translations: HSV + SV</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.2</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Added color option for bible references</li>\n<li>Added language: Portuguese</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.1</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Added exclude HTML elements feature</li>\n<li>Script is loaded async and defer</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>WordPress implementation of <a href=\"https://bible-link.globalrize.org\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">BibleLink</a> plugin by GlobalRize.</li>\n<li>WPML configuration</li>\n</ul>\n"
    },
    "short_description": "This lightweight plugin makes Bible references on your website interactive and supports multiple languages.",
